Text: Displaying Blotter DealsBen Blotter has a selection that needs to be checked in order to display EOL deals The system shows that you dont have that check box checked If thats the problem than all that you need to do is to check that box In Blotter use the Clear button to clear any deals that may already show Go to Defaults on the menu Select the only option there StartupNew Deals Defaults Make sure you have Show EOL Deals checked If this is not the issue please give me a call at Thanks Nikolay Embedded Picture Device Independent Bitmap
